These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, rock, punk, country, house, jazz
6 different pets are kept: dog, pony, snake, chinchilla, bird, goat
 1. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 3. the fan of house is not the owner of the bird##6
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5
 5. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
 7. the owner of the bird is not the fan of rock##6
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the fan of country##7
10. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
11. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
12. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
13. the owner of the dog is the fan of ambient##1
14. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
15. the fan of jazz is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | country   | ambient | punk   | jazz     | rock    | house   |
| Pet           | bird | dog   | goat | chinchilla | snake | pony |

