.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: western, animation, adventure, zombie, action, martial-arts
6 different pets are kept: pony, rat, lizard, hedgehog, cat, frog
 1. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 7. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 8. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching action movies is not the owner of the cat##6
10. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the hedgehog##7
11. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
14. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
15. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
16. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
17. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person watching action movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | zombie | action     | adventure      | western |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard        | cat   | hedgehog | pony | frog    |

