.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, almond-milk, milk, sprite, iced-tea
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, volleyball, badminton, biathlon, snowboarding
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person drinking milk##6
 5. the person drinking coffee is not the person who's sport is rugby##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking 7up##7
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
14. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | sprite        | milk | iced-tea    | coffee    | almond-milk | 7up |
| Sport      | skiing | biathlon  | snowboarding | badminton | rugby | volleyball      |

