12. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person driving the snowmobile##7
13. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | fish   | hamster | ferret      | hedgehog | pony  | turtle   |
| Transport   | roller | van  | snowmobile | bike   | scooter | quad-bike |

