.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, writing, cooking, dancing, sudoku, skydiving
The people have 6 different jobs:  engineer, manager, librarian, videographer, entrepreneur, teacher
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the videographer and the manager##7
 5. the teacher is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the entrepreneur##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
 8. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 9. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
10. the manager is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
11. the teacher is on the right of the librarian##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the videographer##5
13. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
14. the manager is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
15. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | cooking         | dancing | writing | chess   | skydiving | sudoku  |
| Job     | entrepreneur | videographer  | librarian  | teacher | manager  | engineer |

 